Hi.

50:32.047 --> 50:33.214
Hey, lady.

50:34.214 --> 50:36.214
Oh. Let's get you a drink.

50:36.297 --> 50:39.339
-What do you feel like?
-Oh, um, I like Chardonnay.

50:39.422 --> 50:40.756
Chardonnay, please.

50:42.673 --> 50:44.756
Well. Oh, perfect.

50:46.839 --> 50:48.589
I thought
you were gonna text me earlier.

50:48.673 --> 50:52.214
Oh, yeah. Well, I--
I got caught up, uh, you know,

50:52.297 --> 50:54.422
-watching the Nuggets.
-Oh.

50:55.005 --> 50:56.464
You look great.

50:57.381 --> 50:59.631
Oh. I do?

50:59.714 --> 51:03.214
Uh-huh. It was fun last night.

51:07.381 --> 51:09.381
And we can have fun again.

51:22.547 --> 51:27.547
So, how was, uh, scuba diving?

51:27.631 --> 51:29.506
Uh... I don't know.
