51:30.923 --> 51:32.172
I wanna wait for you.

51:34.506 --> 51:35.923
You do?

51:36.005 --> 51:38.339
The guy said
we could go out tomorrow.

51:39.589 --> 51:40.631
Wow.

51:41.673 --> 51:43.214
It hurts to smile.

51:44.130 --> 51:46.047
How bad does it look?

51:46.130 --> 51:47.464
It looks cool, Dad.

51:48.339 --> 51:49.631
You look like a badass.

51:49.714 --> 51:53.881
Yeah?
-Yeah, Dad. You saved Mom.

51:54.631 --> 51:57.589
You're a total stud.

51:57.673 --> 52:00.506
I don't know about that.

52:21.172 --> 52:22.839
Goodbye.
Yeah.

52:22.923 --> 52:25.798
Oh, I'm leaving super early,
so you won't see me,

52:25.881 --> 52:27.964
but I love you guys.

52:28.047 --> 52:30.923
I'm so happy I got to see you.

52:31.005 --> 52:32.631
You're such a gorgeous couple,

52:32.714 --> 52:36.172
you have so much going for you,
so be happy, okay?

52:36.631 --> 52:37.881
Just be happy.

52:38.714 --> 52:40.756
-I love you.
-I love you, darling.

52:40.839 --> 52:42.089
Thanks for coming.

52:45.839 --> 52:47.381
Be happy, Rachel.

52:48.631 --> 52:49.964
Okay?

52:53.839 --> 52:55.047
I love you, guys.

52:55.130 --> 52:56.714
And I'll tell Cathy
you say hi!

52:56.798 --> 52:59.214
And enjoy Tahiti!
I'm so jealous!

52:59.297 --> 53:00.923
Yeah. Travel safe.

53:01.005 --> 53:02.964
Love you, Mom.
-That was such a nice dinner.

53:15.589 --> 53:19.881
(STUTTERS, GRUNTS) Greg, Greg.

53:30.964 --> 53:31.964
What?

53:35.673 --> 53:36.798
Greg, come on.

53:39.464 --> 53:40.798
You need to go.

53:41.964 --> 53:45.214
What? Why?

53:45.297 --> 53:49.547
Well, you know, eventually,
you're just gonna leave.

53:49.631 --> 53:52.839
So I think we should just cut
to the chase.

53:52.923 --> 53:54.381
Okay? Let's just go.

53:54.464 --> 53:56.047
Huh?
-Okay. We need to go now.

53:56.130 --> 53:59.464
What?
-Yeah, I mean it.

54:02.464 --> 54:05.881
I'm a very needy person,

54:05.964 --> 54:10.130
and I am deeply,
deeply insecure.

54:10.923 --> 54:12.172
-This is--
-Hmm.

54:12.255 --> 54:16.214
Both my parents
mentally abused me and--

54:16.297 --> 54:21.964
and-- and my mother still
tortures me, and she's dead.

54:22.047 --> 54:26.297
And I still have her ashes.
I carry them around.

54:35.089 --> 54:39.464
So now you see,
that's the core of the onion.

54:42.673 --> 54:45.673
It's already--

54:46.339 --> 54:47.464
This is it.

54:47.547 --> 54:51.547
This is the core of the onion,
and I don't want to--

54:51.631 --> 54:54.673
I want you to get out of here
and save yourself

54:54.756 --> 54:58.130
because I'm just like a--
I'm like a dead end, you know?

54:58.214 --> 55:02.381
This is a trap door.
And I think you should get out.

55:02.464 --> 55:04.297
And I want you
to take these things.

55:04.381 --> 55:05.547
-Whoa.
-I want you take 'em.

55:05.631 --> 55:07.839
I want you to get out
of here now!

55:07.923 --> 55:09.881
The f-- I'm not gonna take
your dead mother's ashes.

55:09.964 --> 55:11.506
I want you to get them
out of here.

55:11.589 --> 55:13.172
What the fuck am I supposed
to do with them?

55:13.255 --> 55:15.130
I don't know. Put them
in the trunk of your car.

55:15.214 --> 55:16.547
Just get them out of here.

55:16.631 --> 55:18.297
You can put them in a trashcan.

55:18.381 --> 55:20.798
-You're fucking crazy.
-It's who I am.

55:20.881 --> 55:22.964
And I-- There's nothing
I can do about it.

55:23.047 --> 55:28.339
Please get out.
Please. Get out.

55:28.422 --> 55:31.339
Greg, I told you
to get the fuck out.

55:33.214 --> 55:34.214
No.

55:37.214 --> 55:38.756
I still wanna fuck you.

55:45.089 --> 55:48.547
Really?

55:50.547 --> 55:51.589
Yeah.

55:56.255 --> 56:00.130
