eat every night

57:21.839 --> 57:24.547
makes me wanna gouge
my eyes out.

57:28.381 --> 57:29.798
The Lotus-eaters.

57:36.506 --> 57:38.839
"Hateful is the dark-blue sky,

57:39.673 --> 57:42.506
