1:01:22.130 --> 1:01:22.964
My hero.

1:01:24.964 --> 1:01:26.839
You were on fire last night.

1:01:29.631 --> 1:01:30.881
<i>I'm not going home.</i>

1:01:31.255 --> 1:01:32.589
What are you doing?

1:01:33.673 --> 1:01:34.464
Texting.

1:01:34.547 --> 1:01:35.589
Texting who?

1:01:41.255 --> 1:01:44.714
<i>I'm realizing I'm getting back
into this pattern again.</i>

1:01:45.005 --> 1:01:46.381
It's not healthy.

1:01:46.756 --> 1:01:49.089
<i>We are starting
down a very dark road.</i>

1:01:49.589 --> 1:01:52.255
Why are you ruining everything?

1:01:54.798 --> 1:01:56.589
<i>Is this like
a kamikaze situation?</i>

1:01:56.673 --> 1:01:58.047
Are you gonna
take me down with you?

1:01:58.464 --> 1:01:59.923
<i>I'm getting fired.
